    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely gotta see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken incredible care of it, and it's in truly pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for its next home, this is the one. I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have, so don't be shy!",
