    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen retains its factory-spec structural rigidity and features a crisp 6-speed manual transmission paired with the M Variable Differential Lock. Meticulously maintained, the double-VANOS system operates flawlessly, and the rod bearings have been serviced preventatively. The chassis is free of oxidation, with all bushings and multi-link suspension components providing a factory-tight damping profile. A truly concours-level example for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
