    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom-quality condition since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with professional ceramic coating and absolutely zero stone chips, dings, or scratches. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and the original 'new car' scent still lingers. Every switch, dial, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive binder of records to prove its pampered life. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain or inclement weather. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the finest example available on the market today.",
